You need to strip them manually.

```
def get_text(html):
    tree = HTMLParser(html)

    if tree.body is None:
        return None

    for tag in tree.css('script'):
        tag.decompose()
    for tag in tree.css('style'):
        tag.decompose()

    text = tree.body.text(separator='\n')
    return text
```

